section.section:
The Commission shall adopt by regulation on or before December 1, 1985 criteria for program development and approval, which are necessary or appropriate to achieve the standards stated in subsection (b) of this section. Prior to developing its criteria and also prior to adopting its criteria, the Commission shall hold at least 6 regional public hearings, 1 in each of the following areas:
Harford, Cecil, and Kent counties;
Queen Anne's, Talbot, and Caroline counties;
Dorchester, Somerset, and Wicomico counties;
Baltimore City and Baltimore County;
Charles, Calvert, and St. Mary's counties; and
Anne Arundel and Prince George's counties.
